subSubSection.paragraph:
Description. Male (Manaus,
21-30 .x. 1997
). Head. Dorsal part of the eye yellow to light brown, with large ommatidia; ventral part of the eye black, with small ommatidia. Subcallus brown with gray pollinosity. Base of antenna with dense silver gray pollinosity. Antenna brown; scape with mixed black and white hairs; pedicel with black hairs; flagellum with golden pollinosity. Basal flagellomere with dorsal spine reaching the second flagellomere. Face and parafacia dark brown with dense silver pollinosity and yellow hairs. Gena and postgena dark brown with dense silver pollinosity and yellow hairs. Palpus light brown with sparse gray pollinosity and mixed black and yellow hairs.

Measurements. (n = 1 , Manaus,
21-30 .x. 1997
) Body length: 12.71mm . Wing length: 9.71mm .
